=== TASK ===
Ticket: AGT-265
Title: [AUTO] Agent spawns sub-agent for large tasks
Priority: medium
Status: backlog

Description:
## Goal

When ticket is too large, agent splits into sub-tasks and spawns parallel workers.

## Trigger

* Ticket has >3 files to change
* Ticket has multiple components
* Agent detects "and" in requirements

## Implementation

1. Agent analyzes ticket
2. Creates sub-issues in Linear
3. Dispatches to other agents
4. Waits for completion
5. Merges results

## North Star

Parallel execution - 4 agents = 4x speed.

=== DISPATCH RULES ===
- Commit with "closes AGT-265" when done
- Push immediately after commit
- Leave Linear comment: files changed, what was done
